@startuml
Here is the corrected PlantUML:

title UML state machine diagram

state Idle
Idle : entry/To action
Idle : do/Remain in same state
Idle : exit/Login / Register

state Register
Register : entry/Register
Register : do/Register after validating
Register : exit/Login/Invalid registration

state InvalidRegistration
InvalidRegistration : entry/Invalid registration
InvalidRegistration : do/Cannot register
InvalidRegistration : exit/Abnormal termination

state Login
Login : entry/Login
Login : do/Login using valid username and password
Login : exit/Invalid login/To home page

state InvalidLogin
InvalidLogin : entry/Invalid login
InvalidLogin : do/Cannot login
InvalidLogin : exit/Abnormal termination

state ReadBlog
ReadBlog : entry/To home page
ReadBlog : entry/Read blogs of recovered patients
ReadBlog : exit/Idle

state UpdateCurrentNoOfInfectedPeople
UpdateCurrentNoOfInfectedPeople : entry/To home page
UpdateCurrentNoOfInfectedPeople : do/Update current no. of infected people in the locality
UpdateCurrentNoOfInfectedPeople : exit/View

state ViewNumberOfInfectedPeopleInTheLocality
ViewNumberOfInfectedPeopleInTheLocality : entry/View
ViewNumberOfInfectedPeopleInTheLocality : do/View number of infected people in the locality
ViewNumberOfInfectedPeopleInTheLocality : exit/Idle

state NoOfDeathsInTheLocality
NoOfDeathsInTheLocality : entry/View
NoOfDeathsInTheLocality : do/View no. of deaths in the locality
NoOfDeathsInTheLocality : exit/Idle

state ViewMaskDemand
ViewMaskDemand : entry/View
ViewMaskDemand : do/View mask demand in the locality
ViewMaskDemand : exit/Stock

state StockUp
StockUp : [valid] entry/Stock
StockUp : do/Stock up masks and gloves by the shops
StockUp : exit/End

state SendPatientInfo
SendPatientInfo : entry/To home page
SendPatientInfo : do/Update data by home quarantined patients
SendPatientInfo : exit/View patient info

state ViewPatientInfo
ViewPatientInfo : [valid] entry/View patient info
ViewPatientInfo : do/View patient info by the medical professional
ViewPatientInfo : exit/Prescribe

state PrescribeMedicinesIfNeeded
PrescribeMedicinesIfNeeded : [valid] entry/Prescribe
PrescribeMedicinesIfNeeded : [valid] do/Prescribe medicines if needed
PrescribeMedicinesIfNeeded : exit/View data from doc

state ViewDataSharedByDoctor
ViewDataSharedByDoctor : [valid] entry/View data from doc
ViewDataSharedByDoctor : do/View data shared by doctor
ViewDataSharedByDoctor : exit/Buy medicines

state ListAllMedicalShops
ListAllMedicalShops : entry/To home page
ListAllMedicalShops : do/List all medical shops in the locality
ListAllMedicalShops : exit/Buy medicines

state AssignCorporationWorker
AssignCorporationWorker : [valid] entry/To home page
AssignCorporationWorker : [valid] do/Assign workers to disinfect in an area
AssignCorporationWorker : exit/Update status

state UpdateStatusOfCleanliness
UpdateStatusOfCleanliness : [valid] entry/Update status
UpdateStatusOfCleanliness : do/Update status of cleanliness in the locality
UpdateStatusOfCleanliness : exit/End

state BuyMedicines
BuyMedicines : [valid] entry/Buy medicines
BuyMedicines : [valid] do/Buy medicines if needed
BuyMedicines : exit/End

state J1 <<choice>>
[*] --> Idle
Idle --> Register
Register --> Login
Login --> J2
J2 --> InvalidLogin
J2 --> ReadBlog
J2 --> UpdateCurrentNoOfInfectedPeople
J2 --> SendPatientInfo
J2 --> ListAllMedicalShops
J2 --> AssignCorporationWorker
J2 --> PrescribeMedicinesIfNeeded
@endum
@enduml
